 2015\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Josh Taylor (actor)|Josh Taylor]]\n| Chris Kositchek\n| 1977\u20131987\n|-\n| [[Roman Brady]]\n| 1997\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Paul Telfer (actor)|Paul Telfer]]\n| [[Xander Kiriakis]]\n| 2015\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Greg Vaughan]]\n| [[Eric Brady]]\n| 2012\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Robert Scott Wilson]]\t\n| [[Ben Weston (Days of Our Lives)|Ben Weston]]\t\n| 2014\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[Arianne Zucker]]\n| [[Nicole Walker]]\n| 1998\u20132006, 2008\u2013present\n|-\n| Helena Tasso\n| 2016\n|-\n| Kristen DiMera\n| 2019\n|}\n\n=== Recurring cast ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:50%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Actor\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Character\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Duration\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[John Aniston]]\n| Eric Richards\n| 1970\n|- \n| [[Victor Kiriakis]]\n| 1985\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Julian Barnes\n| Harold \n| 2009\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Sydney Brower\n| [[Arianna Horton]]\n| 2019\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Laura Kai Chen\n| Melinda Trask\n| 2013, 2016\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[George DelHoyo]]\n| Orpheus\n| 1986\u201387, 2016, 2020\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Billy Flynn (actor)|Billy Flynn]]\n| [[Chad DiMera]]\n| 2014\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Bill Hayes (actor)|Bill Hayes]]\n| [[Doug Williams (Days of Our Lives)|Doug Williams]]\n| 1970\u20131984, 1986\u20131987, 1993\u20131996, 1999\u2013present\n|-\n| Byron Carmichael\n| 1979\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Leann Hunley]]\n| [[Anna DiMera]]\n| 1982\u20131986, 2007\u20132010, 2017\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | Brock Kelly\n| Josh\n| 2005\u20132006\n|-\n| Evan Frears\n| 2019\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Ron Leath\n| [[Henderson (Days of Our Lives)|Henderson]]\n| 1987\u20132004, 2008\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Harlow & Scarlett Mallory\n| Holly Jonas\n| 2018\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Kate Mansi]]\n| [[Abigail Deveraux]]\n| 2011\u20132016, 2018\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Thaao Penghlis]]\n| [[Tony DiMera]]\n| 1981\u20131985, 2007\u20132009, 2019\u2013present\n|-\n| [[Andr\u00e9 DiMera]]\n| 1983\u20131984, 1993\u20131996, 2002\u20132005, 2007, 2015\u20132019\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[James Read]]\n| [[Clyde Weston]]\n| 2014\u20132017, 2019\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Susan Seaforth Hayes]]\n| [[Julie Olson Williams]]\n| 1968\u20131984, 1990\u20131994, 1996, 1999\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | William Utay\n| Wilhelm Rolf\n| 1997\u20132003, 2007\u20132008, 2017\u2013present\n|}\n\n== Cast changes ==\n<!-- ONLY INCLUDE INFORMATION OBTAINED FROM RELIABLE SOURCES. AVOID BLOGS AND FAN-SITES: INFORMATION IS FALSIFIED AND UNRELIABLE. -->\n=== Debuting ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:50%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Actor\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Character\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Date\n! style=\"width:10%;\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Remington Hoffman\n| Li Shin\n| April 22, 2020\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |last=Cushman |first=Dustin |title=Remington Hoffman Joins ''Days'' as Li Shin from ''Chad & Abby in Paris'' |url=https://soaps.sheknows.com/days-of-our-lives/comings-and-goings/553052/remington-hoffman-joins-days-li-shin/ |website=[[Soaps.com]] |publisher=[[SheKnows Media]] |accessdate=November 11, 2019 |location=United States |date=November 8, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Rachele Schank\n| Juliet\n| {{TableTBA}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |last=Bowe |first=Jillian |title=''Days of Our Lives: The Digital Series'' to Launch on The DOOL App August 1 |url=https://daytimeconfidential.com/2019/07/29/days-of-our-lives-the-digital-series-to-launch-on-the-dool-app-august-1 |website=[[Daytime Confidential]] |publisher=