ring]]\n| [[Rafe Hernandez]]\n| 2020\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |last=Fix |first=Christine |title=Galen Gering Shares That His Days are Numbered as Rafe Hernandez |url=https://soaps.sheknows.com/days-of-our-lives/comings-and-goings/558975/galen-gering-shares-that-his-days-are-numbered-as-rafe-hernandez/ |website=[[Soaps.com]] |publisher=[[SheKnows Media]] |accessdate=February 7, 2020 |location=United States |date=February 6, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=SOD |authorlink=Soap Opera Digest |title=Galen Gering Marks End of ''DAYS'' Run |url=https://www.soapoperadigest.com/content/galen-gering-marks-end-of-days-run/ |website=[[Soap Opera Digest]] |publisher=[[American Media, Inc.]] |accessdate=February 14, 2020 |location=United States |date=February 14, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Returning ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:50%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Actor\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Character\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Date\n! style=\"width:10%;\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Alyshia Ochse\n| Zoey\n| April 2020\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |last=Young |first=Candace |title=Alyshia Ochse Returns to ''Days'' as New Character for Multi-Episode Spring Arc |url=https://soaps.sheknows.com/days-of-our-lives/comings-and-goings/561542/alyshia-ochse-returns-days-new-character-zoey/ |website=[[Soaps.com]] |publisher=[[SheKnows Media]] |accessdate=March 23, 2020 |location=United States |date=March 16, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Louise Sorel]]\n| [[Vivian Alamain]]\n| July 2020\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |last1=Silver |first1=Carly |title=Louise Sorel Checks Back in to ''Days of Our Lives'' |url=https://daytimeconfidential.com/2019/12/30/louise-sorel-checks-back-in-to-days-of-our-lives |website=[[Daytime Confidential]] |publisher=[[SAY Media|Confidential Media, Inc.]] |accessdate=December 31, 2019 |location=United States |date